@startuml

state "Waiting for Amount Selection" as WaitingAmount
state "Custom Amount Entry" as CustomEntry
state "Transaction Verification" as Verify
state "Re-enter Amount" as ReEnter

[*] --> WaitingAmount

WaitingAmount --> CustomEntry : enter custom value
WaitingAmount --> Verify : select from options

Verify --> Verify : reject, re-enter amount -> ReEnter
Verify --> [*] : transaction successful

@enduml
